{"tid":1344580,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"＠入村有伏，要小心","createTime":"2019-07-21T23:46:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T23:48:43.000Z","uid":269761,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"480aae37b79b38cb7cdb10d748234d702b8080f4","tid":1344580,"uid":269761,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:46:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">其實，佢地在明，要揸正來做。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">各區鄉事委員會</span></strong></span>經常有大人小朋友聚會，但有可能有危險品，有啤酒樽加白毛巾，有白色粉末，仲有白衫... <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">石門是新界鄉議局</span></strong></span>的總部，間中有會開，不過有記者。通常開完會佢地去食飯，食得好好。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">鄉村嘅祠堂</span></strong></span>真係好緊要嘅地方，但係保養差，成日被啲流浪動物搗亂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.hyknt.org\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hyknt.org&d=D9%2BIkncl4BF5lZ8wPV9kyLhWJNg3BDkm8i4jVfgHOzw%3D&h=df89983b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.hyknt.org</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n記住，戰線太多未必係好事。"},{"pid":"43b63dd99ee5d534df76912b10a7b1daa9b0dbe5","tid":1344580,"uid":29218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T23:48:43.000Z","msg":"應儘快民間普選<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1340757\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1340757</a>"}]}